tMonsterGroup = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_VGN_TravelingScholar_Ambush")

-- Run to the center
for i, idMonster in pairs(tMonsterGroup) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonster) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idMonster) then
		Hydra.ActorSetAITether(idMonster, marker_tether)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	tSpawners = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "spawners")
	
	for i=1, #tSpawners do
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(tSpawners[i])
		Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	end
end
